title: 55: Car Dealerships in Fargo, ND
description:
Happy podversary!! We're celebrating one year of Beach Too Sandy nonsense! Thank you so much for your support this past year. As a special gift, we've finally revealed the identity of the man behind our intro. And no, it's not Bosephus! So go watch our latest YouTube video to see that reveal: https://youtu.be/l8Qzn-kW2wY
Support us on Patreon at patreon.com/beachtoosandy for a livestream Q&A every month. 
Buy our merch! https://store.dftba.com/collections/beach-too-sandy-water-too-wet

Music by PSOVOD and tyops.
